    <section id="abt" class="about home-about-cont">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row mb-40">
                <div class="col-sm-7">
                    <h2 class="about-title"><i class="fa fa-align-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> About US</h2>
                    <p class="mb-40">We’re headquartered in Mumbai, providing supply chain, logistics management and distribution channel, spread over the states of Bihar, Jharkhand, West Bengal, Maharashtra and Odisha and expanding rapidly nationally.</p>
                    <h2 class="about-title"><i class="fa fa-align-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> Ashoka Group Of Enterprises</h2>
                    <p>The foundation of this group was laid in the late 1980’s by our founder Shri Ashok Kumar Poddar in Darbhanga Bihar.</p>
                    <p>With his vision, mission and hard work the group is now a leading name for supply chain and logistics with increasing presence nationally.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-5">
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="images/about-us-img.jpg" alt="Founder Photo">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row mb-40">
                <div class="col-sm-12">
                    <h2 class="about-title"><i class="fa fa-align-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> Group Statistics</h2>
                    <ul class="common-ul">
                        <li><i class="fa fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> The Group volumes are 8 Lakh MT Rake/Cargo Handling and Transportation of 15 Lakh MT of Cement on an average per annum.</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> The Group processes approx 1000 orders per day.</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> The Group caters to approx 1500dealers and retailers on a daily basis.</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> Group also expedites in handling and transportation of Clinker, Gypsum, and Aggregates.</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> The Group is involved in construction activity for warehouses, buildings and bridges.</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> The Group is coming up with its logistics park with E2E facility located at the INDIA-NEPAL trade corridor.</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> The Group is coming up with a Slag grinding unit in Surat (Guj) for production of GGBS.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="images/founder-img.jpg" alt="Founder Photo">
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <h2 class="about-title mb-40"><i class="fa fa-align-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> FOUNDER</h2>
                    <h3 class="about-title-small">SHRI ASHOK KUMAR PODDAR</h3>
                    <p class="mb-20">A professional graduate with 30 + years of experience in transportation, Clearing & forwarding activities, Ware house management and sales of Cement, Paint, TMT bars, Chemicals and other construction related products.</p>
                    <p class="mb-20">Our founder started this business as a small cement retailer, who used his two-wheeler to move in the lanes of Darbhanga with a single bag of cement in search of customers.</p>
                    <p class="mb-20">Later on having taken a hand loan from his father of Rs. 4lakhs at 15% interest in 1984-85 and starting a retail outlet in by the name of Ashoka Enterprises. Very soon the firm became a reputed name in the retail market for building
                        materials.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
