            <h1 align="center">Our Approach</h1>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="col">
                    <img src="media/discover.png" alt="">
                    <h3>Discover</h3>
                    <p>Good questions lead to great creatives. Thus every brief deserves to be nudged, questioned and sometimes need to be broken. It’s how we uncover new opportunities meaningful truth that defines a project success story. We start by testing
                        assumptions and dive into deep understanding of you and those you serve - a foundation of forward thinking strategist that guides your project success. </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="col">
                    <img src="media/create.png" alt="">
                    <h3>Create</h3>
                    <p> Impactful brands thrive at the intersection of clarity and purposes. Your brand should reflect your voice, values and standards more than a style guide.</p>
                    <p>
                        By bringing brand character and strategy to the forefront, our creative efforts focus on emotion throughout the brand experience. </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="col">
                    <img src="media/iterate.jpg" alt="">
                    <h3>Iterate</h3>
                    <p> Is it relevant, compelling and actionable? Precisely, we hustle with an absolute focus on detail, carefully honing brand interactions until they produce the greatest amount of conversions.</p>
                    <p>Our creative process is supported by an iterative, adaptable and measured approach that design to deliver results. </p>
                </div>
